evidence.text: This application translates cutscenes in Fate/Grand Order JP & NA into a variety of different languages. It features real time machine translation of the most recent event using [DeepL](https://www.deepl.com/). Older content uses the official translation from the North American region. Teams of translators are working on human translations in various different languages.
2. Log into Fate/Grand Order JP to ensure your game data is up to date - click "Download" if promoted for a data update. Afterwards, close the application.
